<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:59:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美军拦截俄罗斯和中国飞机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-intercepts-russian-chinese-aircraft-2024-07-25/</link><description>美国军方周三表示，拦截了在阿拉斯加防空识别区飞行的两架俄罗斯和两架中国军用飞机，尽管它们仍在国际空域。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:41:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-military-intercepts-russian-chinese-aircraft-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>台风“嘉美”掠过台湾，登陆中国沿海</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</link><description>台风“嘉美”周四席卷台湾北部，带来洪水并导致交通拥堵，随后跨海进入中国大陆，预计将带来进一步的暴雨。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:29:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/typhoon-gaemi-passes-over-taiwan-heads-chinese-coast-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国主要银行在降低贷款利率后降低存款利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</link><description>在中国下调基准贷款利率几天后，包括中国工商银行（ICBC）和中国农业银行（AgBank）在内的几家中国主要银行周四宣布下调定期存款利率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/major-chinese-banks-cut-deposit-rates-after-reduction-lending-rates-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>专家称，中国的秘密航天飞机可能正在测试“双重用途”技术</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</link><description>专家表示，中国的无人可重复使用航天器在火箭助推器顶部发射，降落在一个秘密军用机场，很可能是在测试技术，但也可用于操纵或回收卫星。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jul 2024 00:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/space/chinas-secretive-spaceplane-likely-testing-dual-use-technology-experts-say-2024-07-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国告诉跨国公司台湾员工不要违法，没什么好害怕的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dont-break-law-you-have-nothing-fear-china-tells-taiwan-staff-multinational-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国政府周三表示，在华跨国公司的台湾员工只要不违法就没有什么好担心的，因为新的法律指导方针要求在极端情况下处决“顽固”分裂分子。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:06:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/dont-break-law-you-have-nothing-fear-china-tells-taiwan-staff-multinational-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>日经新闻报道本田将削减在中国的内燃机汽车产能</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-honda-slash-gas-cars-production-capacity-china-nikkei-says-2024-07-24/</link><description>据《日经新闻》周四报道，汽车制造商本田汽车计划将内燃机汽车的产能削减三分之一，因为来自低价本土制造商的竞争加剧对日本汽车制造商的销售造成压力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automaker-honda-slash-gas-cars-production-capacity-china-nikkei-says-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>意大利总理梅洛尼本周将访华并提出贸易和投资议程</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</link><description>一位参与计划的人士告诉路透社，意大利总理乔治亚·梅洛尼将于7月26日至31日访问中国，这是她上任以来的首次访问，旨在改善与中国的贸易。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 16:44:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/italys-meloni-visit-china-this-week-with-trade-investment-agenda-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>美国对帮助朝鲜的中国网络实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</link><description>美国财政部表示，美国周三对一家帮助朝鲜发展弹道导弹和太空计划的中国网络实施制裁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 15:33:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-imposes-sanctions-china-based-network-helping-north-korea-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国钢铁贸易商寻求推迟新螺纹钢标准的实施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-steel-traders-seek-delay-new-rebar-standards-2024-07-24/</link><description>贸易商和分析师表示，中国地区钢铁贸易协会正在寻求推迟颁布新的建筑用螺纹钢质量标准，该标准计划于 9 月 25 日实施的消息引发了库存抛售。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 13:12:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinese-steel-traders-seek-delay-new-rebar-standards-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>奥的斯因中美建筑活动放缓下调年度销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</link><description>由于北美和中国对其新设备的需求疲软，电梯制造商奥的斯环球公司 (Otis Worldwide) 周三下调了 2024 年净销售额预期。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 12:08:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/otis-cuts-annual-sales-view-slowdown-construction-activity-china-us-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，印度可能放松对部分中国投资的限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</link><description>两位政府消息人士称，印度可能会放松对中国在太阳能电池板和电池制造等非敏感行业投资的限制，而新德里缺乏专业知识，这阻碍了国内制造业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 10:48:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-likely-ease-curbs-some-chinese-investments-sources-say-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，中国比亚迪在新加坡和东南亚的电动汽车市场上扩大了对特斯拉的领先优势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</link><description>政府数据显示，今年上半年，中国比亚迪在新加坡扩大了对特斯拉的销量领先优势，凸显了这家全球最大电动汽车制造商在中国竞争对手销量方面面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 09:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-widens-ev-lead-over-tesla-singapore-southeast-asia-data-shows-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>雷米首席财务官表示，尚未给出对中国白兰地调查做出决定的日期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</link><description>在顶级干邑生产商上周参加了有关该问题的听证会后，人头马君度首席财务官周三表示，北京方面尚未给出对欧盟白兰地反倾销调查做出决定的官方时间表。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:51:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/remy-cfo-says-no-date-yet-given-decision-china-brandy-probe-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯指责美国加剧北极紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</link><description>俄罗斯周三指责华盛顿加剧北极紧张局势，并驳斥了美国军方关于俄罗斯和中国在该地区加强合作可能影响地区稳定的说法。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:40:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-accuses-us-stoking-tensions-arctic-2024-07-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国成立党领导的反腐委员会以金融业为目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-financial-sector-with-party-led-anti-graft-committee-2024-07-24/</link><description>中国任命了一名反腐官员领导一个新的委员会来打击金融领域的腐败，这表明执政的共产党正在加强对这个拥有66万亿美元资产的行业的控制。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 08:28:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-targets-financial-sector-with-party-led-anti-graft-committee-2024-07-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>